  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink231-kilavi">oruvaḻit taṇantu vanta talaimakaṉ nāṉ pirinta nāṭkaṇ nīr eṉ ceytīr eṉak kēṭkat tōḻi avaṟkuc colliyatu.</p>
        <p xml:lang="en"> What the confidante told the hero who had gone away briefly and returned, when he asked, “What did you do during the days I was separated [from you]?” 
        </p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink232">
<l>pōtār kūnta liyalaṇi yaḻuṅka</l>
<l>vēti lāḷaṉai nīpirin tataṟkē</l>
<l>yaḻalavir maṇippū ṇaṉaiyap</l>
<l>peyalā ṉāveṉ kaṇṇē teyyō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>As the natural beauty</l>  
        <l>[of her whose] tresses are full of buds</l> 
        <l rend="indent2">is being spoiled,</l> 
        
        <l rend="space">O stranger, because you have separated,</l>
        <l rend="indent">as [my] ornaments, [whose] gems shine [like] fire, become wet,</l>
        <l rend="indent">my eyes do not cease from weeping — alas.</l>
        
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
